<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>LYBSO™ — Fiche Métier · Bien-être & Santé Naturelle</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400;1,500&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--vert:#052f31;--sauge:#5e6c5a;--clair:#b0b59e;--beige:#e3e0d7;--creme:#f8f6ef;--blanc:#ffffff}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;background:var(--creme);color:var(--vert);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden}
@media print{.no-print{display:none!important}.page{page-break-after:always;min-height:auto;padding:40px}.hero{min-height:auto;padding:60px 40px}}
.progress-bar{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;height:2px;background:var(--beige)}
.progress-fill{height:100%;background:var(--sauge);width:0%;transition:width .1s}
nav{position:fixed;top:2px;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(5,47,49,.97);padding:0 48px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.nav-logo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--creme);text-decoration:none}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:6px}
.nav-links a{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair);text-decoration:none;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:1px;transition:all .2s}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{background:var(--sauge);color:var(--creme)}
.nav-print{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--sauge);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:1px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.nav-print:hover{background:var(--sauge);color:var(--creme)}
.hero{min-height:100vh;background:var(--vert);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:120px 80px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'🌿';position:absolute;right:-30px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-size:360px;opacity:.03;pointer-events:none;line-height:1}
.hero-inner{max-width:780px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair);margin-bottom:6px;display:block}
.hero-phase{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:28px;display:block}
.hero h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(42px,6vw,72px);font-weight:300;color:var(--creme);line-height:1.06;margin-bottom:20px}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--clair)}
.hero-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--clair);line-height:1.9;max-width:540px;margin-bottom:40px}
.hero-metiers{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin-bottom:40px}
.mtag{font-size:10px;color:var(--clair);background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;cursor:default;transition:all .2s}
.mtag:hover{background:rgba(94,108,90,.2);border-color:var(--sauge);color:var(--creme)}
.mon-metier{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(94,108,90,.4);border-radius:2px;padding:18px 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.mon-metier label{font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);white-space:nowrap}
.mon-metier input{flex:1;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:var(--creme);font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:300;font-style:italic;padding:4px 0;outline:none}
.mon-metier input::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.15)}
.mon-metier input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--sauge)}
.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:36px;left:80px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;animation:bob 2.5s infinite}
.scroll-hint span{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--clair);text-transform:uppercase}
.scroll-line{width:36px;height:1px;background:var(--sauge)}
@keyframes bob{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:.4}50%{transform:translateY(5px);opacity:1}}
.page{min-height:100vh;padding:96px 80px}
.page-creme{background:var(--creme)}
.page-beige{background:var(--beige)}
.page-vert{background:var(--vert)}
.page-blanc{background:var(--blanc)}
.plabel{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);display:block;margin-bottom:10px}
.page-vert .plabel{color:var(--clair)}
.ptitle{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,50px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;color:var(--vert);margin-bottom:14px}
.ptitle em{font-style:italic;color:var(--sauge)}
.page-vert .ptitle{color:var(--creme)}
.page-vert .ptitle em{color:var(--clair)}
.pdivider{width:36px;height:1px;background:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:40px}
.psub{font-size:13px;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.9;max-width:580px;margin-bottom:56px}
.page-vert .psub{color:var(--clair)}
.erreurs{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;max-width:820px}
.erreur{display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr;background:var(--blanc);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;transition:transform .3s}
.erreur:hover{transform:translateX(5px)}
.erreur-n{background:var(--vert);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:300;color:var(--clair)}
.erreur-b{padding:24px 28px}
.erreur-t{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--vert);margin-bottom:8px}
.erreur-d{font-size:12px;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:12px}
.erreur-r{font-size:11px;color:var(--sauge);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px}
.erreur-r::before{content:'→';flex-shrink:0}
.zone-inp{background:rgba(94,108,90,.07);border:1px solid rgba(94,108,90,.2);border-radius:2px;padding:22px 26px;margin-top:40px;max-width:820px}
.zone-inp label{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);display:block;margin-bottom:10px}
.zone-inp textarea{width:100%;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(5,47,49,.12);font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:17px;font-style:italic;color:var(--vert);resize:none;outline:none;padding:8px 0;line-height:1.6;min-height:52px}
.zone-inp textarea::placeholder{color:rgba(5,47,49,.2)}
.profils{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;margin-bottom:56px}
.profil{padding:36px 32px;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid transparent;transition:all .3s;position:relative}
.profil.p-prat{background:var(--blanc)}
.profil.p-coach{background:var(--creme)}
.profil:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
.profil.sel{border-color:var(--sauge)}
.profil-badge{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:12px;display:block}
.profil h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:400;color:var(--vert);margin-bottom:10px}
.profil p{font-size:12px;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:12px}
.profil-metiers{font-size:10px;color:var(--clair);font-style:italic;line-height:1.7}
.profil-btn{margin-top:18px;font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:9px 18px;border:1px solid var(--sauge);background:transparent;color:var(--sauge);border-radius:1px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.profil-btn:hover,.profil.sel .profil-btn{background:var(--sauge);color:var(--creme)}
.profil-check{position:absolute;top:18px;right:18px;width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--sauge);color:var(--creme);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
.profil.sel .profil-check{opacity:1}
.arbre{max-width:820px}
.arbre-lbl{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:24px;display:block}
.arbre-q{background:var(--blanc);border-radius:2px;padding:22px 26px;margin-bottom:14px;display:none}
.arbre-q.vis{display:block;animation:fi .4s ease}
.arbre-qt{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:20px;color:var(--vert);margin-bottom:14px}
.arbre-opts{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.arbre-opt{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:20px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--beige);background:var(--creme);color:var(--sauge);transition:all .2s}
.arbre-opt:hover{border-color:var(--sauge);color:var(--vert)}
.arbre-opt.sel{border-color:var(--vert);background:var(--vert);color:var(--creme)}
.niche-res{background:var(--vert);border-radius:2px;padding:32px;display:none;margin-top:20px}
.niche-res.vis{display:block;animation:fi .5s ease}
.niche-lbl{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair);margin-bottom:10px;display:block}
.niche-res h4{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:26px;color:var(--creme);margin-bottom:8px}
.niche-res p{font-size:12px;color:var(--clair);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px}
.niche-cible{font-size:11px;color:var(--clair);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.niche-cible::before{content:'✦';color:var(--sauge)}
.niche-transfo{margin-top:14px;padding:14px 18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-left:2px solid var(--sauge);font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:17px;font-style:italic;color:var(--creme);line-height:1.6}
@keyframes fi{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.offre-tabs{display:flex;margin-bottom:36px}
.offre-tab{padding:10px 24px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:var(--beige);color:var(--sauge);transition:all .2s}
.offre-tab.act{background:var(--vert);color:var(--creme)}
.offre-tab:first-child{border-radius:1px 0 0 1px}
.offre-tab:last-child{border-radius:0 1px 1px 0}
.offre-panel{display:none}
.offre-panel.act{display:block;animation:fi .3s ease}
.offre-ex{background:var(--blanc);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:36px;max-width:820px}
.offre-hdr{background:var(--vert);padding:26px 32px}
.offre-etag{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}
.offre-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:300;color:var(--creme);margin-bottom:4px}
.offre-tagline{font-size:12px;color:var(--clair);font-style:italic}
.offre-body{padding:32px}
.offre-includes{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:28px}
.incl{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;font-size:12px;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.6}
.incl::before{content:'✦';color:var(--sauge);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;font-size:9px}
.offre-diff{background:rgba(94,108,90,.08);border-left:2px solid var(--sauge);padding:18px 22px}
.offre-diff-t{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}
.offre-diff p{font-size:12px;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.8}
.tarif-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;max-width:820px;margin-bottom:36px}
.tarif{padding:26px 22px}
.t1{background:var(--creme)}.t2{background:var(--beige)}.t3{background:var(--vert)}
.tarif-lbl{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;display:block}
.t1 .tarif-lbl,.t2 .tarif-lbl{color:var(--sauge)}.t3 .tarif-lbl{color:var(--clair)}
.tarif-price{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:300;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px}
.t1 .tarif-price,.t2 .tarif-price{color:var(--vert)}.t3 .tarif-price{color:var(--creme)}
.tarif-desc{font-size:11px;line-height:1.7}
.t1 .tarif-desc,.t2 .tarif-desc{color:var(--sauge)}.t3 .tarif-desc{color:var(--clair)}
.offre-perso{max-width:820px}
.offre-perso-lbl{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:16px;display:block}
.offre-perso-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:14px}
.inp-f{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.inp-f label{font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair)}
.inp-f input{background:var(--blanc);border:1px solid var(--beige);border-radius:1px;padding:10px 14px;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:15px;font-style:italic;color:var(--vert);outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.inp-f input:focus{border-color:var(--sauge)}
.inp-f input::placeholder{color:rgba(5,47,49,.18)}
.objections{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;max-width:820px}
.obj{background:var(--blanc);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.obj-btn{width:100%;text-align:left;background:none;border:none;padding:24px 28px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px}
.obj-q{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:19px;color:var(--vert);font-style:italic}
.obj-icon{color:var(--sauge);font-size:20px;transition:transform .3s;flex-shrink:0}
.obj-btn.open .obj-icon{transform:rotate(45deg)}
.obj-body{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .4s ease,padding .3s;padding:0 28px}
.obj-body.open{max-height:360px;padding:0 28px 24px}
.obj-sig{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}
.obj-mean{font-size:12px;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px}
.obj-rlbl{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--vert);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}
.obj-rep{background:var(--creme);border-left:2px solid var(--sauge);padding:14px 18px;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:16px;font-style:italic;color:var(--vert);line-height:1.6}
.obj-perso{margin-top:10px}
.obj-perso label{font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair);display:block;margin-bottom:5px}
.obj-perso input{width:100%;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--beige);padding:7px 0;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:15px;font-style:italic;color:var(--vert);outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.obj-perso input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--sauge)}
.obj-perso input::placeholder{color:rgba(5,47,49,.18)}
.hooks-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;max-width:820px}
.hook-pilier{background:var(--blanc);border-radius:2px;padding:28px}
.hook-pilier.span2{grid-column:1/-1}
.pilier-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:18px}
.p-aim .pilier-badge{background:rgba(5,47,49,.07);color:var(--vert)}
.p-rev .pilier-badge{background:rgba(94,108,90,.1);color:var(--sauge)}
.p-sto .pilier-badge{background:rgba(176,181,158,.2);color:var(--sauge)}
.hook-item{margin-bottom:18px;padding-bottom:18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--beige)}
.hook-item:last-child{margin-bottom:0;padding-bottom:0;border-bottom:none}
.hook-sujet{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--vert);margin-bottom:6px}
.hook-txt{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:15px;font-style:italic;color:var(--sauge);line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:var(--creme);border-left:2px solid var(--sauge);margin-bottom:7px}
.hook-cp{font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sauge);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.hook-cp:hover{opacity:.6}
.hook-cp.copied{color:var(--clair)}
.plan-tl{max-width:700px}
.plan-w{display:grid;grid-template-columns:88px 1fr;gap:0;margin-bottom:2px}
.plan-wn{background:var(--sauge);padding:24px 18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:2px}
.plan-wlbl{font-size:7px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(248,246,239,.6)}
.plan-wnum{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:34px;font-weight:300;color:var(--creme);line-height:1}
.plan-wb{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);padding:24px 28px}
.plan-wtheme{font-size:8px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--clair);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}
.plan-wtitle{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:20px;color:var(--creme);margin-bottom:10px}
.plan-acts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.plan-act{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px}
.plan-chk{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);flex-shrink:0;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;margin-top:2px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.plan-chk.done{background:var(--sauge);border-color:var(--sauge)}
.plan-chk.done::after{content:'✓';color:white;font-size:9px;font-weight:600}
.plan-atxt{font-size:12px;color:var(--clair);line-height:1.7}
.cta-final{background:var(--sauge);padding:44px 80px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:32px}
.cta-txt h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:300;color:var(--creme);margin-bottom:6px}
.cta-txt p{font-size:12px;color:rgba(248,246,239,.6);line-height:1.7}
.cta-links{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-shrink:0}
.cta-btn{padding:12px 24px;border-radius:1px;font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;white-space:nowrap}
.cta-dark{background:var(--vert);color:var(--creme)}
.cta-dark:hover{background:#021e20}
.cta-light{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--creme);color:var(--creme)}
.cta-light:hover{background:var(--creme);color:var(--sauge)}
@media(max-width:768px){nav{padding:0 20px}.nav-links{display:none}.hero,.page{padding-left:24px;padding-right:24px}.hero{padding-top:96px}.profils,.offre-includes,.hooks-grid,.offre-perso-grid,.tarif-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.hook-pilier.span2{grid-column:auto}.plan-w{grid-template-columns:64px 1fr}.cta-final{flex-direction:column;padding:44px 24px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="prog"></div></div>
<nav class="no-print">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">LYBSO™</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#erreurs">Erreurs</a><a href="#niche">Niche</a><a href="#offre">Offre</a><a href="#objections">Objections</a><a href="#contenu">Contenu</a><a href="#plan">Plan</a>
  </div>
  <button class="nav-print" onclick="window.print()">Imprimer</button>
</nav>

<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="hero-eyebrow">Fiche Métier LYBSO™ · 01 / 08</span>
    <span class="hero-phase">Phase B+S — Brand & Strategy · Clôture Semaine 7</span>
    <h1>Bien-être &<br><em>Santé Naturelle</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">Tu as ton offre, ton prix, ta marque et ton Content Engine™. Ce guide t'aide à tout appliquer concrètement dans la réalité de ton secteur — avec des exemples précis, des fourchettes réalistes et des mots exacts à utiliser. Juste avant de lancer ton Sprint.</p>
    <div class="hero-metiers">
      <span class="mtag">Naturopathe</span><span class="mtag">Sophrologue</span><span class="mtag">Hypnothérapeute</span><span class="mtag">Réflexologue</span><span class="mtag">Acupunctrice</span><span class="mtag">Herboriste</span><span class="mtag">Aromathérapeute</span><span class="mtag">Nutritionniste</span><span class="mtag">Coach en nutrition</span><span class="mtag">Ostéopathe libérale</span><span class="mtag">Sage-femme libérale</span><span class="mtag">Praticienne ayurvédique</span><span class="mtag">Médecine traditionnelle chinoise</span>
    </div>
    <div class="mon-metier">
      <label>Mon métier précis</label>
      <input type="text" placeholder="ex : Sophrologue spécialisée anxiété" id="monMetier">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint no-print"><div class="scroll-line"></div><span>Défiler</span></div>
